metadata.name: Project ZND #1
metadata.description: Zombiesnotdead - that’s the 3333 pixel zombies, we’re raise from dead to take the revenge and be knowable in the world! ZND NFT is your key that allows you to get involved into our ecosystem. We just started building culture and legacy of zombies. By the way every holder of ZND project automatically being Co-Founder. We’re looking for build something special in this kinda market, besides closed alpha community, giveaways and alpha calls, we’re looking for Twitter AMAs with influencers and founders of hype alphas/projects. That’s why we’re gonna make fully interaction with community. Let’s get attention on zombies or zombies will catch you. CCO!
